reviews.review_text: This fast food serves good clean food. Theyre busy but they keep everything clean.  Theyre wonderful and kind. Ms. Gurpreet, Tanvir, Gurleen, Harnid? a supervisor, one by one are all polite and attentive. I like this place because they give five star service in a fast food setting.  I honor them.
FROSTY is my favorite icy treat of all time  and always vanilla for me. Only 99 cents in summer!

Store was clean and staff is well trained it was an rush hour and they try there best to help all . Managers are cooperative and helping . I like the food as well as the Wendy s atmosphere. I will definitely visit again.

Service was great! Food was delicious! And Ravi was great at making sure our dining experience was fulfilled! Making sure we got what we ordered. Which was what the picture looked like he made sure we got the right meal prepared! Booyah! Food : 5/5
I really like Wendys atmosphere rather than McDonalds. It is really quiet neat and also has better food. Food

This place is open for DINE IN! Probably the cleanest Wendys I have ever seen! Probably updated so NOICE ONE! They arranged the tables and chairs for social distancing. Will come back again even fries are too salty.

I came here after hiking the grouse grind and ordered this unholy abomination of my own creation: its a half pound baconator with a crispy chicken patty on top. One would think such a hunger craving would be disgusting and yet it was one of the most delicious things Ive ever had, and the staff passed zero judgement on me for ordering it. Wendys is truly a place where I can be me.

they have baked potatoes about half of the time better than most stores I think. may they should cook half a batch at a time so there are potatoes every half hour  instead of none for an hour or once half are sold cook another batch might be an idea..

I didnt stay to eat. I did the quick takeout. Had a great bowl of chili and cheese. Less than $4 I really enjoyed it. I usually have the spicy chicken  burger. Those are great. Parking: They have their own lot, but BMO is adjacent to it. I went in there. Kid-friendliness: Every time Im there, kids are enjoying kid meals. They have a good selection of salads too. Wheelchair accessibility: They have wheelchair accessibility in the west side.
Thank you for always fresh and fast warm food . Hardworking employees and kind.
Its a Wendys.  Not much else to say lol But I love it, and never had an issue with the service Food
Food was made perfect and the new bbq bacon cheeseburger is amazing
The burger was delicious. And Im always so glad to have such a variety of sugar free sodas available to me as a diabetic. The staff was really friendly and the atmosphere was warm and clean...

Wendys provided me with an impressive dining experience. The food had good taste and great texture - the burger patties were good quality and nicely cooked and the fries were very crisp. Everything was clean, and it was relaxing. Ill recommend it to others - my only regret is that I live far away.

The food is fresh and tasty. Very nice staff as we arrived quite late there and the store was about to close, the staff accepted our order with smile although they looked to have a very busy day. Thank you and well be there again
First Wendys McDonalds or a&w Ive enjoyed in years.   Tasted like real food... almost

Went through the drive through on Monday at 9pm. The lady taking the order was a bit scattered, probably busy, there was a few cars in line. Ordered 3x Jr Bacon Cheeseburgers and Nuggets. Absolutely amazing. Food was hot, bacon was nice and crispy! Highly recommended.
One exception...They need to correct one of their ads,the picture shows a big burger,but theyre promoting a junior burger..
The best Wendys Ive gone to.

Nice seating area. Not just a large open space.  Good job from Wendys designers. Good food at reasonable price. A friend loved the Berry Burst Salad. Also has two soft drink machine.  Can even get sparkling water from it.

Try the spicy chicken and spicy fries, its great!  This Wendys is operated well, and never disappoints.  Keep up the good work! I recommend this location. With that said, the property management in charge of the parking lot sucks.  They left a pot hole so big, that it damaged cars and trucks for weeks before it was repaired!  This has nothing to do with Wendys, but Wendys management should take it up with their landlord, since its their customers being impacted.  If you go to this location, just be careful of the potholes!  Biggest one Ive hit to date, and probably threw off my alignment, if not cracked my rim. Highly recommended otherwise!
Great food but the drive thru is chaotic.  I have seen fights of people cutting others off waiting to merge from different directions.  Best burgers out there and the lemonade is great.

I ordered a combo burger today. I was really surprised how their burger and fries are so good and tasty. It s much better than McDonald s burgers. I loved it. Thanks to Wendys for a tasty,  yummy and excellent size and value for your meals.
Best hamburger I ve ever eaten. A lot of kind of drinks as well, and the fries are perfect (could be larger)

On a super cold and rainy day my family and I  ordered drive though. I called to complain when I got home and told them I was coming back, as they gave us a wrong burger. When I got there, not only did I get my correct burger, they thanked me for coming back in the bad weather, gave me a full refund and a free frosty! I am used to expecting bad customer service from a fast food chain nowadays, but this was exemplary. Well done on the customer service front!

I usually drive through, but came in this time.  They had the baconator for $5  in a limited time promotion.  Overall, this fast food chain really does make a tastier burger than other chains.  Im a pickle fan, but not a fan of Wendys pickles.  Not sure if anyone else feels the same way.
Nice staff & Delicious foods
My first time eating at this location. It was very clean and fast service. The staff were exceptionally nice and kind. I recommend this Wendys to everyone
I ve been visiting this Wendy s for over 10 years now. The food is always fantastic, fries and fresh, and service is good.

I was parked in traffic waiting to get onto the bridge for a couple of hours.   I saw a few people leave their cars and get food in the slow traffic.   They seemed happy.  Im vegan so I hope Wendys gets a plant based option soon so that I could have given them some business
This restaurant is Amazing because of its fantastic level of service.   Young man Jeremy delivers five star service in a fast food place.   Im so grateful.

Lets be very clear for all of my fellow foodies out there - this restaurant is not fast food or even quick service.  This is a highly tailored, streamlined dining experience.  Personally, I was lucky to get in due to the size of the line.  I might have had to mention I was an influencer *wink wink* on both Yelp! and Instagram (TM). When you enter, ask the matre-d what the chef recommends that day.  During my visit it was the Spicy Chicken Sandwich and I was informed there was a limited run based on available farm-to-table ingredients.  Boy was I lucky - it was prepared fresh by the gifted young chef, Braydon, and promptly brought to me by an extremely professional waiter Ghazal. The plating was impeccable, as if the foil was designed for my personal sandwich itself.  Absolutely to die for.  The sauce must be truffle infused because it was heavenly.  The bun was clearly artisan, I think from a local bakery on Lonsdale.  The tomato had to have been grown that day and I could ABSOLUTELY tell that the chicken used to make the sandwich was the alpha of the roost.  A prime specimen, surely. I cannot say enough positive things about this experience.  I will be returning, that is, if I am lucky enough to get in again *wink wink*! Please follow me on Yelp! to take part in my food journey!!!!!

Of all the burger chains, Wendys is my favorite because of the Baconator. This particular location is a bit hard to find the first time. The drive-through entrance is unusual, but the lines are usually short, the service fine, and the quality consistent.
Got a junior bacon cheeseburger and a junior deluxe burger..around $5.00 all up. Great deal and the burgers were very good.
Is the best hamburguers fast food in Vancouver! The quality of the food is good and also the flavor. Price is good! And the staff is super fast
Amazing. Fast food
Best Wendys Ive been to. Burgers are cooked to perfection and the special drink dispenser provides 18 different options. My go to place when craving Wendys.
Best chain burgers in my opinion. Big, tasty and right price. This place have a drive thru and close late so it is very convenient.
Good food. Love the brioche buns, the spicy chicken burger and of course the chocolate frosty
I have never had a bad experience with this restaurant. The service is always so good, and the food is exactly what I expect it to taste like.
They get 5 stars because they let me mix my frosty flavours without giving me a hard time about it.
crispy bacon and good patti ...plus fluffy bread
Fast and friendly service. The dining area was very clean.
The best chicken fingers. Real meat, not ground and overprocessed. Finally a breakfast menu!!
Super good burgers and fries (malts are cheap and super tasty as well), regular fast food prices, and nice interior styling. I wish there were more of these around!
Theyre a lot quicker than other Wendys Ive been to!  Staff are super nice too.
Same great taste I have come to expect at Wendys. I only eat their Chicken burgers though. I dont eat burgers that arent char- broiled
Its a Wendys. The only downside is that its not closer to my house.

The baconator is really amazing here.
Love it. The food was great with a great view which included a bear on the other side of the river
Welcoming friendly atmosphere. Professional employees, very clean good taste food.
This place is clean, fast, and friendly. Its a little hard to find if you dont look hard enough.
Service ok some of Burgers are ok make sure your order is right.
Havent had baconator in a while! It was definitely judgement day of tastiness
Quality Wendys, serving quality food. Open dining room during coronavirus, how novel.
Saturdays I like to go to Wendys for the Daves Double and Poutine..nothing could be finer than that meal
Spicy chicken overpriced and not as good as it used to be
OMG I luvvvvvvv Wendys!!! Food super delicious and the meals are affordable
The remodel came out great. Always love the food.
Newly renovated, very nice, and with the 100 flavor Coke machines!
Good service and food is always tasting fresh
Best fast food love a jbc and a chocolate frosty
new breakfast wedges are so good wow
Baked                                    potatoes very good. Thanks Wendy. Also very good borger

Love their summer salad. I wait all year long for it come out
